profiles/ExpansionMod/**/Backup/**
profiles/ExpansionMod/**/Backups/
profiles/ExpansionMod/**/Backups/**

# Never publish game binaries, Steam files, Workshop mods, keys, profiles, logs, caches, or persistence.
@*/
